        "title": "지방자치단체 공유재산 및 물품 관리 조례 - 광역자치단체별 링크 모음",
        "date": "2026-04-13",
        "views": 0,
        "content": "<p><strong>공유재산 및 물품 관리법</strong>에 근거하여 각 지방자치단체에서 제정·운영하고 있는 <strong>공유재산 및 물품 관리 조례</strong>를 광역자치단체별로 정리하였습니다. 각 링크를 클릭하면 해당 조례 본문으로 이동합니다.</p><h4>근거 법령</h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.law.go.kr/LSW/lsInfoP.do?lsiSeq=245281\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">공유재산 및 물품 관리법</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.law.go.kr/LSW/lsInfoP.do?lsiSeq=273567\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">공유재산 및 물품 관리법 시행령</a></li></ul><h4>특별시 · 광역시 · 특별자치시</h4><table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\"><thead><tr style=\"background:#f5f5f5;\"><th style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:left;\">지방자치단체</th><th style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:left;\">국가법령정보센터</th><th style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:left;\">자치법규정보시스템</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\">서울특별시</td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.law.go.kr/LSW/ordinInfoP.do?ordinSeq=2099991\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">공유재산 및 물품 관리 조례</a></td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.elis.go.kr/allalr/allAlrList?ctpvCd=11&sggCd=000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">서울 자치법규</a></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\">부산광역시</td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.law.go.kr/LSW/ordinInfoP.do?ordinSeq=2064537\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">공유재산 및 물품 관리 조례</a></td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.elis.go.kr/allalr/allAlrList?ctpvCd=26&sggCd=000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">부산 자치법규</a></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\">대구광역시</td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.law.go.kr/자치법규/대구광역시+공유재산+및+물품+관리+조례\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">공유재산 및 물품 관리 조례</a></td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.elis.go.kr/allalr/allAlrList?ctpvCd=27&sggCd=000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">대구 자치법규</a></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\">인천광역시</td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.law.go.kr/LSW/ordinInfoP.do?ordinSeq=1970341\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">공유재산 관리 조례</a></td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.elis.go.kr/allalr/allAlrList?ctpvCd=28&sggCd=000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">인천 자치법규</a></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\">광주광역시</td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.law.go.kr/LSW/ordinInfoP.do?ordinSeq=1544557\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">공유재산관리 조례</a></td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.elis.go.kr/allalr/allAlrList?ctpvCd=29&sggCd=000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">광주 자치법규</a></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\">대전광역시</td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.law.go.kr/자치법규/대전광역시+공유재산+관리+조례\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">공유재산 관리 조례</a></td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.elis.go.kr/allalr/allAlrList?ctpvCd=30&sggCd=000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">대전 자치법규</a></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\">울산광역시</td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.law.go.kr/LSW/ordinInfoP.do?ordinSeq=1266795\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">공유재산 관리 조례</a></td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.elis.go.kr/allalr/allAlrList?ctpvCd=31&sggCd=000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">울산 자치법규</a></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\">세종특별자치시</td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.law.go.kr/LSW/ordinInfoP.do?ordinSeq=1545787\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">공유재산 관리 조례</a></td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.elis.go.kr/allalr/allAlrList?ctpvCd=36&sggCd=000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">세종 자치법규</a></td></tr></tbody></table><h4>도 · 특별자치도</h4><table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\"><thead><tr style=\"background:#f5f5f5;\"><th style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:left;\">지방자치단체</th><th style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:left;\">국가법령정보센터</th><th style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:left;\">자치법규정보시스템</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\">경기도</td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.law.go.kr/LSW/ordinInfoP.do?ordinSeq=1404190\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">공유재산관리 조례</a></td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.elis.go.kr/allalr/allAlrList?ctpvCd=41&sggCd=000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">경기 자치법규</a></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\">강원특별자치도</td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.law.go.kr/자치법규/강원특별자치도+공유재산+관리+조례\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">공유재산 관리 조례</a></td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.elis.go.kr/allalr/allAlrList?ctpvCd=42&sggCd=000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">강원 자치법규</a></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\">충청북도</td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;\"><a href=\"https://www.law.go.kr/자치법규/충청북도+공유재산+관리+조례\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">공유재산 관리 조례</a></td><td style=\"padding:8px 12p